videos.description: Tennessee's Lamonte Turner gets open with a nice crossover dribble and delivers the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Turner crosses and drills it from downtown

videos.description: Tennessee's Derrick Walker spins past his defender in the post and lays it off the glass.
videos.headline: Walker shows off the post moves

videos.description: Tennessee's Derrick Walker gets the dump off pass from Lamonte Turner and dunks it home.
videos.headline: Walker throws down the one-handed slam

videos.description: Tennessee's Lamonte Turner makes a nice defensive play and Yves Pons finishes it with a transition dunk.
videos.headline: Steal leads to a Vols slam

videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams rises up for a monster slam in the face of two South Carolina defenders.
videos.headline: Williams throws it down over two Gamecocks

videos.description: Wesley Meyers drills a deep three to spark South Carolina late in the second half.
videos.headline: Meyers keeps the Gamecocks in it

videos.description: Beth Mowins and Jimmy Dykes sit down with Lamonte Turner who dropped a career-high 25 points in another SEC win for Tennessee.
videos.headline: Turner leads Tennessee to a big road win at USC
